		<h1>Solo Mining 101</h1>

		<p class="text-sm" style="margin-top:-10px;margin-bottom:14px;">
			A simple guide to what the stats mean in a solo pool.
		</p>

		<div class="panel-stack">
			<div class="overview-banner" style="margin-bottom:0;">
